channel.title: Which client has correct Godwars NPC?
channel.description:
Hi, I've been searching for a good client that loads the correct Godwars NPC's. All the ones i download load the dwarf banker dude for General Graardor and the other dwarfs for his minions...
Any help is appreciated!

item.title: Which client has correct Godwars NPC?
item.dc:creator: @u_loose u loose
item.description:
@u_loose wrote:

[quote=“iBucky, post:3, topic:529291”][quote author=u loose link=topic=648047.msg4358941#msg4358941 date=1378270993]

Hi, I’ve been searching for a good client that loads the correct Godwars NPC’s. All the ones i download load the dwarf banker dude for General Graardor and the other dwarfs for his minions…

Any help is appreciated!

Varrockscape has correct models, but doesn’t have the dungeon
[/quote]

Thanks, I Tried with VarrockScape client, Whenever I spawn a Godwars NPC it crashes my client. 6260 for example (General Graardor)[/quote]

I’ve never had that problem, and I’ve been using varrockscape for a while now
